{
  "stem": "27150.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, that means we were stopping at farms and the places we had to walk, there was a group of eight at that time, this time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the places we had to walk, we had to go in one other's steps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, so that means if somebody passes through the snow, that one man was going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then for the route, we took a whole sled and so the wind blew down the snow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then at the next farm, we took a wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the wheels were frozen, the metal was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we ended up, you see, the three women were sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the five man, you see that we ended up pushing the wagon or the sled.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we came to a little township on the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was the last station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was New Year's eve.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We're sitting in-- you see, some of the farmers were sleeping on benches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My coat was frozen to the window, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But somehow-- you know, it was an experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then on the New Year, we came to a place a few steps to the border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the locals actually could cross the borders, because they were families broken up, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the idea was that they sent a couple of women with big bags of flax.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You see, it's big and easy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were crossing the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And if the guards pick them and take them to the station, the border is free.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we'll run over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were waiting, you see, with the watches on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the same women came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There's nobody on the border.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because they're celebrating the New Year on the station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Run.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
